{"tid":1079964,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救/求教］我架車好騎呢","createTime":"2019-03-27T09:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T13:18:15.000Z","uid":87687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f89a3481ddcc2bf8b5bdec2a3a7a63ed90929e66","tid":1079964,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"我架係echo verso. 好好用好實用好可靠。<br />\n<br />\n不過佢有個問題，就係入油果時會不停咁彈油槍。好撚on9咁。<br />\n<br />\n去過唔同油站，唔同油槍都係咁，肯定係我架車既問題。我網上搵唔到資料（或者我搵唔啱key word). 但好似個個油站職員都 &ldquo;哦。。。又係呢種&rdquo; 咁既表情。我懷疑唔係咁旱有。<br />\n<br />\n問車房又係標準&ldquo;拎來拆開睇睇先知咩事喎&rdquo;既標準劏人起手。<br />\n<br />\n求助萬能既連登仔，知唔知大概咩料，有冇得整整幾錢左右？"},{"pid":"5ff7562f3c0d605cdf181c0ebb3549c83bcf3372","tid":1079964,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebbd10a4c36b779bb58c1743889e43fe0c49f4c","tid":1079964,"uid":72085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"咁唔拆又真係唔知咩事喎，除非佢整過"},{"pid":"cf5dffe653afbc5097c66723ea524a2a3b284b0d","tid":1079964,"uid":182127,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"部車絶食"},{"pid":"094bcdd09f07893f7d027812ca28c7c039fd67f3","tid":1079964,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"油喉空氣氣壓問題。"},{"pid":"14fffd206fdb89ba64db7872ccc65f21c31a3fb4","tid":1079964,"uid":208241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"似係油缸個vent/evap返引擎嗰到有事"},{"pid":"79ae831fa96401b876a5d848014d9c09c7cba992","tid":1079964,"uid":15714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"試下叫油站職員用慢槍入"},{"pid":"4deeca6b3621b5c593ddd29d5dd74c14ce1a6b56","tid":1079964,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14fffd206fdb89ba64db7872ccc65f21c31a3fb4","tid":1079964,"uid":208241,"like":1,"dislike":0